auth {
  mode: bearer
}

auth:bearer {
  token: {{apiKey}}
}

docs {
  # st0r4g9

  A simplified, S3-flavored object store. Run `Create API Key` first — its
  post-response script stores the returned key into the `apiKey` environment
  variable, and every other request inherits `Authorization: Bearer {{apiKey}}`
  from this collection. Then walk the requests top to bottom (they are ordered
  via `seq`): create a bucket, put an object, get/list/query it, then clean up.
}
